# Cloudflare Pages headers for the Common Place Book web build.
#
# Ensure WebAssembly is served with the correct MIME type so the browser can
# stream-compile it. Without this, WASM instantiation can fail.
/*.wasm
  Content-Type: application/wasm

# OPFS (the most durable drift storage) requires the page to be cross-origin
# isolated, which needs the two headers below. They are intentionally left
# COMMENTED OUT: enabling cross-origin isolation can break loading of non-CORS
# third-party assets (fonts, images, analytics, etc.). drift falls back to
# durable IndexedDB persistence without them, which already satisfies the
# "survives reload" requirement.
#
# To opt into OPFS later (after confirming all third-party assets send CORS
# headers), uncomment these and pass `moveExistingIndexedDbToOpfs: true` to
# WasmDatabase.open in lib/core/database/connection/web.dart:
#/*
#  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
#  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
